title: Spinach, Leek and Cannellini Bean Soup
ingredients: ['2 teaspoons olive oil', '4 leeks, bulb only, chopped', '2 cloves garlic, chopped', '800ml chicken stock', '2 (400g) tins cannellini beans, rinsed and drained', '2 bay leaves', '2 teaspoons ground cumin', '7 tablespoons couscous', '60g fresh spinach', 'salt and pepper to taste']
